pd_1_com_0text: What? It is just a lowely human.
pd_2_com_0text: I'll teach you a lesson about messing with other people's business. You're almost as laughable as that lowely wizard from not that long ago.
pd_4_com_2text: Make the Demon join your side.
pd_5_com_0text: I do actually see the next Dark Lord in your. I have decided, I will join your side once you take over the world.
pd_6_com_0text: Thank you for freeing me from this cursed form.
pd_7_com_0text: The Evil Dragon Kholin took away my humanity,  I am eternily grateful.
pd_8_com_0text: I'll see you in hell, foul creature.
pd_9_com_0text: Prepare yourself for your next fight with my previous master, Evil Dragon Kholin. I doubt he'll be willing to give up his status as current Dark Lord.
